    help {
        helpText:
            ```html
            
            Use the filters on the left to show different results in the region on the right. The right region can be displayed in one of three ways (Cards View, Report View, and Customizable Grid) by using the display-mode buttons located just to the left of the <strong>Manage Territories</strong> button. Filters are not displayed in the Customizable Grid view.
            ```
